" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 470px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Color flow Doppler of severe aortic regurgitation",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 291px; height: 220px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    The color flow Doppler image is obtained from the transverse view of a transesophageal echocardiogram. The outflow tract is completely occupied by the aortic regurgitant color flow jet (AR jet); when the jet exceeds 65 percent of the left ventricular outflow tract (LVOT) width, the regurgiation is judged severe.",
